<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Landing Page Kamu</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;}

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .hero {
            height: 90vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4CAF50, #81C784);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            background: white;
            color: #4CAF50;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 60px 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .feature-box {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .cta {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        footer {
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        @media(max-width: 768px){
            .features {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .hero h2 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Brand Kamu</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">Fitur</a>
        <a href="#">Kontak</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <div>
        <h2>Solusi Terbaik untuk Masalah Kamu</h2>
        <p>Tingkatkan produktivitas dan hasil dengan layanan kami.</p>
        <button class="btn">Mulai Sekarang</button>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Kenapa Pilih Kami?</h2>
    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Mudah Digunakan</h3>
            <p>Interface sederhana dan user-friendly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Efektif</h3>
            <p>Membantu meningkatkan hasil secara signifikan.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Terpercaya</h3>
            <p>Sudah digunakan oleh banyak pengguna.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
    <h2>Siap Mulai?</h2>
    <p>Gabung sekarang dan rasakan manfaatnya.</p>
    <button class="btn">Daftar Sekarang</button>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Brand Kamu. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
